{"word":"G5548 - χρίω - chríō - khree'-o - Anoint","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χρίω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chríō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khree'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Anoint</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அபிஷேகம் பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"1. consecrating Jesus to the Messianic office"},{"paragraph":"2. enduing Christians with the gifts of the Holy Spirit"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably akin to <a href=\"#/G5530 - χράομαι - chráomai - khrah'-om-ahee/5530\">G5530</a> through the idea of <i>contact</i>; to <i>smear</i> or <i>rub</i> with oil, that is, (by implication) to <i>consecrate</i> to an office or religious service: - anoint.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G500/500\">G500</a>, <a href=\"#/G5545/5545\">G5545</a>, <a href=\"#/G5546/5546\">G5546</a>, <a href=\"#/G5547/5547\">G5547</a>, <a href=\"#/G5548/5548\">G5548</a>, <a href=\"#/G5580/5580\">G5580</a>"}]}